%N A016144 Inverse of 2135th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A016144 Periodic with period length 2135. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A016144 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A016144/b016144.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..3000</a>
%H A016144 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 2135.
